### Create a new book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Lord of the Rings",
  "author": "J.R.R. Tolkien",
  "genre": "Fantasy"
}

### Get all books
GET http://localhost:8080/books?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json

### Get a book by id
GET http://localhost:8080/books/1
Accept: application/json

### Update a book
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Simplicidade e funcionalidade camionham juntos",
  "author": "Fabio Vige",
  "genre": "Fantasy OK"
} 

### Delete a book
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/2
Accept: application/json


